text: Yann Aime Kasaï (born 14 April 1998) is a Swiss football player who plays as dorward for Swiss Super League club FC Zürich. ==Professional career== On 5 December 2018, Kasaï joined FC Zürich. made his professional debut for Zürich in a 2-0 Swiss Super League loss to FC Basel on 9 December 2018. ==Personal life== Kasaï was born in Switzerland and is of Congolese descent. ==References== ==External links== * Soccerway Profile * SFV U20 Profile * SFL Profile * SAFP Profile * World Football Profile * FCZ Profile Category:1998 births Category:Living people Category:People from Neuchâtel Category:Swiss footballers Category:Switzerland youth international footballers Category:Swiss people of Democratic Republic of the Congo descent Category:FC Zürich players Category:BSC Young Boys players Category:Swiss Super League players Category:Association football forwards
